{"text":"Use an appropriate format to structure a formal letter of recommendation for a student applying to a prestigious graduate program in computer science.","lang":"en","__index_level_0__":62,"answer":"Хронологија, including the student's background, academic achievements, and potential contributions to the program.\nFormat: A formal letter of recommendation is a written document that provides an endorsement for a student Applying to a prestigious graduate program in computer science. The letter should be written by a person who has knowledge and expertise in the subject of the student's application, such as a teacher, mentor, or professional in their field of study.\nThe letter should provide a detailed description of the student's background, academic achievement, and potential contribution to the program. It should also include the writer's opinion on the student's strength and potential for success in the program.\nWhen writing a letter of recommendation, it is important to use an appropriate format to structure the letter. This includes providing a clear introduction that identifies the purpose of the letter, highlighting the student's background and achievements, and concluding with a statement of support and recommendation.\n\nAn appropriate format for a formal letter of recommendation would involve using a standard template, such as the following:\nIntroduction: Provide a clear and concise introduction that identifies the purpose of the letter, including the student's background, academic achievement, and potential contribution to the program.\nBackground: Describe the student's background, including their academic achievements, extracurricular activities, and any relevant experiences or events.\nAcademic Achievement: Highlight the student's academic achievement, including their academic record, any awards or recognition received, and any relevant academic projects or initiatives.\nPotential contribution: Describe the student's potential contribution to the program, including their potential to make a difference in the program, their ability to excel in the program, and any relevant resources they may bring to the program.\nConclusion: Conclude the letter with a statement of support and recommendation, including any relevant information about the student's character, work habits, and potential for success in the program.\nIn addition to providing a clear and concise introduction, the letter should also provide a detailed description of the student's background, academic achievement, and potential contribution to the program. This will help to provide a comprehensive understanding of the student's qualifications and potential for success in the program.\nBy using an appropriate format to structure a formal letter of recommendation, you can ensure that the letter is well-organized and effectively communicates the student's qualification and potential for success in the program.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
{"text":"Write a compelling product launch announcement email to inform our customers of our new software solution.","lang":"en","__index_level_0__":63,"answer":"Хронологија and its features, highlighting the benefits of the product, and concluding with a call to action for customers to take advantage of this innovative product.\nProduct Launch Announcement Email\nGood day everyone,  I am excited to introduce our new software solution, which is now available to help you improve your workflow and enhance your productivity. Our new product, called Work Time, is designed to provide users with a flexible and efficient way to manage their work activities. With Work Time, you can easily organize your work tasks, prioritize your work goals, and optimize your productivity.\nThe new product offers a range of innovative features that will help you streamline your work process, reduce stress and anxiety, and increase productivity. For example, with Work Time, you can create a schedule that allows you to focus on the most important tasks at any time, allowing you to achieve more in less time. Additionally, with Work Time, you can prioritize your task by identios the most important tasks and eliminate distractions, ensuring that you complete tasks efficiently and effectively.\nWe understand that work can be challenging, especially when it comes to organizing work activities, prioritizing task, and optimizing productivity. That's why we created Work Time, a software solution that provides user with a flexible and efficient way to manage their work activity. With Work Time, you can easily improve your workflow, enhance productivity, and achieve more in less time.\nWe are proud to offer this new product to our customers, as it has helped many people just like you to improve their workflow, enhance their productivity, and achieve more in less time. We believe that everyone deserves to have a product that helps them improve their work activity, and we are committed to providing produ