{"text":"Việc quan sát hành vi của người khác trong một tình huống xã hội có thể cung cấp những manh mối như thế nào về chuẩn mực và kỳ vọng văn hóa?","lang":"vi","__index_level_0__":37,"answer":"Хронологија của người kháng trong một tìnth huống xã hội có thể cung cấ� những manh mối như thế nào về chuẩn mực và kỳ vọng văn hứa.\n\nThese are the things that I can observe and reflect upon in a situation of social injustice, and they are the things that I can use to inform my actions and decisions-making in such situations.\n\nFor example, if I were to observe a situation of discrimination against a person based on their race or gender, I might be able to reflect upon the ways in which that discrimination is rooted in the broader social structures of inequality and oppression. I could think about the ways that those structures shape people's attitudes and behaviors towards the person experiencing the discrimination, and the way that those attitudes and behavior are often unconscious and unintentional.\n\nI could also think about the ways that the experience of discrimination is experienced by the person, and the way that it shapes their sense of identity and self-worth. I could consider the ways that the experience of discrimination is not just a matter of individual prejudice, but is also a result of the broader system of inequality and oppression.\n\nBy reflecting upon these things, I could potentially inform my action and decision-making in a situation of social injustice. For example, I might feel motivated to challenge the broader social structure of inequality and oppression, rather than simply addressing the individual instances of discrimination. I might also be inspired to work with the person who is experiencing the discrimination to help them find their sense of identity and self-worth, and to work towards a more just and equitable society.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
