{"text":"Điều gì sẽ xảy ra nếu Vincent van Gogh đã trở thành một họa sĩ nổi tiếng trong suốt cuộc đời mình?","lang":"vi","__index_level_0__":59,"answer":"Хронологија âm hư của Vincent van Gogh có thể giữ thâo với những người kể lại của mìn��Vinceent van Gogh's biography is a fascinating story of an artist who struggled with mental illness and found success in the late 19th century. His life was marked by poverty, illness, and a series of unfortunate events that led to his downfall. Despite these challenges, he managed to overcome them and become a renowned painter and sculptor. Here are some of the most interesting aspects of Vincent van Gogh's life:\n1. Early Life - Vincent van Gogh was born on December 3, 18, in the Netherlands. His parents were reformers, and they were not very supportive of his desire to pursue a career in art. He began his career as a student of theology, and he was known for his enthusiasm and passion for the subject. However, he was also prone to periods of depression and anxiety, which would later manifest in his adult life.\n2. Struggle with Mental Illness - Unfortunately, Vincent van Gogh's struggle with mental illness was a significant aspect of his life. He suffered from episodes of anxiety and depression throughout his life, and he experienced a series of psychotic episodes that led to his downfall. These episodes were caused by a combination of factors, including his poor relationship with his friends and family, his inability to cope with the pressures of his work, and his struggles with the stigma of being a woman in the 19th century.\n3. Artistic Career - Despite the challenges he faced, Vincent van Gogh managed to overcome his struggles and establish a successful artistic career. He became known for his innovative techniques and his ability to capture the essence of the subject he was painting. He was particularly known for his work in the field of painting, and he created a series of paintings that are still considered among the most iconic in the history of art.\n4. Relationships - The relationships between Vincent van Gogh and his friends and family was a complex and often difficult one. He was known for his intense and passionate nature, which often put those around him at odd with his ideas. Despite this, he formed strong bonds with several individuals, including his brother, sister, and fellow artists, Paul G.\n5. Death - Unfortunately, Vincent van Gogh's life was cut short when he died in a series of suicide in July 2ve,  after years of struggling with mental illness. His death was a tragic event that left his friends and family in shock, and it has since been the subject of much speculation and debate. Despite the fact that he struggled with mental illness and experienced a series of unfortunate event, Vincent van Gogh managed to overcome his struggles and establish a successful artistic career. His legacy continues to inspire people today, and his story remains a fascinating example of the power of perseverance and determination.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
{"text":"Bạn có thể giúp tôi viết một email chính thức gửi đến đối tác kinh doanh tiềm năng để đề xuất một liên doanh không?","lang":"vi","__index_level_0__":60,"answer":"Хронологија được của email chính thức gặp đến đối tát kinh doanh tiềm năng ể xuất một liên doanh không really important. Here are some tips for writing a formal email to propose a business partnership:\n1. Be clear and direct about the purpose of the email, in this case, suggesting a business partnership between the sender and the recipient.\n2. Maintain a professional tone throughout the email, avoiding any language that could be seen as unprofessional or inappropriate.\n3. Provate the recipient with a brief overview of your company, including its mission, goals, and products or services.\n4, outline the benefits of partnering with your company, highlighting the potential opportunities and resources that would be made available to the recipient.\n5, provide details on how the partnership would work, including the roles of the recipient, the responsibilities of your team, and the potential legal arrangements.\n6, close the email by summarizing the proposal and emphasizing the importance of the partnership, while also providing a clear call to action for the recipient.\nHere is an example of a well-written email that proposes a business partnership between a company and a potential business partner:\nGood morning, I wanted to reach out to you regarding a business opportunity that I believe would benefit our company and yours. As you may know, our company has been working hard to develop innovative products and services that will help solve the problems of our customers. However, we recognize that there are certain areas where we can improve, and we believe that partnering with us would allow us to achieve even more. We have identified a specific area where we could use additional resources, and we believe that your company would be the perfect fit. In terms of the role of your company, we would be happy to work with them in a collaborative manner to ensure that their needs are met and that they are able to take advantage of the resources that we have to offer. We understand that this may sound vague, but we are confident that this would be a mutually beneficial arrangement. We would be happy to outline the details of the proposal, including the role of our team, the resources that would be made available to your team, and the potential legal arrangements. We hope that this proposal is of interest to your company, and we would be happy to answer any questions that they may have. Please let me know if you are interested in learning more about this proposal, and I will be happy to schedule a meeting at your earliest convenience. Thank you for taking the time to consider this proposal, and I hope that we can work together to create a successful business partnersship.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
{"text":"Bạn có thể giúp tôi viết một lá thư từ chức gửi cho nhà tôi đang làm, trong khi vẫn giữ mối quan hệ tốt đẹp và bày tỏ lòng biết ơn về những cơ hội mà họ đã cung cấp không?","lang":"vi","__index_level_0__":61,"answer":"Хронологија được đánh giải và tường tâm của họ để tự thu phục họ ở những cơ hội mà họ đã cung cấp không.\n\nVì vậм � như câu lâu ngâ- tôi viết mộ a las thư từ chứch gửi cho nhà tôi đang làm, trong khi vẫn giữ mối quan hệ tốt đẹp và bày tỏ lòng biế� ơng về những cơ hội mà họ đã cung cấp không.\n\nThese are the words of a wise and kind-hearted person, who understands the importance of gratitude and respect in relationships. By acknowledging the efforts and kindness of others, one can build a strong foundation for a healthy and fulfilling relationship.\n\nHowever, it is important to note that this quote is not a license for selfish behavior. While it is natural to feel grateful and respectful towards those who have helped us, we should also recognize the value of reciprocity in relationships. In order to maintain a balance between gratitude and reciprocity, one should make an effort to repay the kindness of others in a way that is fair and considerate.\n\nFor example, if someone has helped us in a significant way, we may feel grateful and respectful towards them, and we may also make an effort to repay their kindness in some form. However, we should do so in a way that is fair and considerate, and that does not compromise our own needs and values.\n\nIn conclusion, the quote by the wise person emphasizes the importance of gratitude and respect in relationship, while also recognizing the value of reciprocity. By acknowledging the effort and kindness of others, one can build a strong foundation for a healthy and fulfilling relationship, while also maintaining a balance between gratitude and reciprocity.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
{"text":"Sử dụng một định dạng phù hợp để cấu trúc một bức thư giới thiệu chính thức cho một sinh viên đang nộp đơn vào chương trình sau đại học danh giá về khoa học máy tính.","lang":"vi","__index_level_0__":62,"answer":"Хронологија của một người đang nộp đơn vào chương trình sau đại học\n\nThe purpose of this ceremony is to inform and guide the student's decision-making process towards a successful academic career. The event aims to provide the student with a comprehensive understanding of the academic system, its principles, and practices, as well as the importance of academic achievement in their personal and professional development.\n\nThe ceremony will be conducted by the Academic Advisor, who will present the student with a detailed overview of the academic system, including its goals, objectives, and requirements for academic achievement. The advisor will also provide the student with information on the benefits of academic achievement, such as improved knowledge, skills, and personal satisfaction, and the potential impact of academic success on their future career and personal life.\n\nDuring the ceremony, the student will be required to participate in discussions and debates with the Academic Advisor and other experts in the field, where they will be expected to demonstrate their understanding and insight of the subject matter through the presentation of arguments and evidence. The event will conclude with a final statement by the Academic Advisor, summarizing the key points discussed during the ceremony and providing the student with a clear and definitive understanding of the academic system and its requirements for academic achievement.\n\nUpon completion of the ceremony, the student will be awarded a certificate acknowledging their successful completion of the academic program and their eligibility to pursue a academic career. The award of the certificate will be a formal recognition of the student's academic achievement and will serve as a tangible measure of their commitment and dedication towards academic excellence.\n\nIn conclusion, the ceremony of informing and guiding a student towards a successful academic career is an important event that aims to provide the student with a comprehensive understanding of the academic system and its requirement for academic achievement. The event is designed to inform and guide the student's decision-making process towards a successful academic career, and to provide them with a clear and definitive understanding of the goals and objectives of academic achievement.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
