eral. The cultural significance of music jazz lies in its ability to reflect the cultural and social context of the society where it emerges, and it has been seen to have a significant impact on the development of music in general. Music jazz has been the object of various study and discussion among music enthusiasts and professionals, and it is expected to continue to be an object of study and discussion in the future.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_zh_zscore|open_ended"}
